casebody.data:
Dennis B. McGUIRE, petitioner,
v.
Norman ROBINSON, Warden. No. 13-8165, 13A720. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 15, 2014.

Case below, 738 F.3d 741.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice KAGAN and by her referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to *999the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.
